5: Shall we rest here for the day?
9:
Huh, is it just me, or is something
going on?
13:
Welcome to the show, ladies and
gents!
16:
Magic's about to happen, so sit
back, relax, and keep your eyes on
me!
20:
Does she plan on performing HERE
of all places?
31:
Wow... I've never seen anything like
that!
36:
Was she manipulating light to make
those effects?
39: Did you have a good time, everyone?
44:
Weeell, if you insist, I've got one
more trick up my sleeve!
53: R-right, we gotta help her out!
57:
What do we have here? More folks
for the show?
62:
Looks like I'll have to kick this show
up a notch for you all!
66:
In the name of the light and all the
rainbows of the world, I'll punish you!
82:
She yeeted those monsters out of
here like it was nothing.
89:
Appreciate ya trying to help me
back there though!
93:
You're a magician of exceptional
ability. Why not cull the monsters
quickly yourself?
99:
Cutting them down would have
been easy for someone with her
level of power and finesse.
103:
Heehee, you'll make a girl blush with
a compliment like that!
106:
As for your question, well... An
illusionist should always put on a
good show!
111:
I see. Respectable enough, I
suppose.
115:
A fellow fun appreciator, I see! Well
have I got an offer for you...
119:
...A once-in-a-lifetime chance to
travel alongside the lovely and foxy
Illumine!
123:
Act now, and we can have a blast all
the way to Palpebra for free!
127:
In other words... You wanna travel
with us to Palpebra?
135:
My audience ran away for some
reason, so now I'm completely broke!
139:
Kind of amazing you can say that
with a smile on your face...
143:
Perhaps you could join us in
Starview?
150:
I was surprised to see someone use
light magic in such a manner...
153:
Which leads me to believe everyone
else might enjoy seeing the show
too.
157:
So what you're telling me is, I've got
a new audience waiting! Count me
in!
164:
Leave the flashy stuff to me! I've still
got a lot more razzle-dazzle up my
sleeves!
